    protected abstract static class AbstractListenerService.AbstractBuilder<B extends AbstractListenerService.AbstractBuilder<B>>
extends AbstractGenericService.AbstractGenericBuilder<B,ListenerProvider,ListenerManager>
implements ListenerService.Builder
    An abstract builder for creating listener service instances.

    Builder instances can be reused, it is safe to call build() multiple times to build multiple listener services in series.
